data.description: This charming, historically renovated home is waiting for you to make it your own! With a nearly new HVAC units downstairs, a recently replaced roof, upgraded cabinets, stunning granite countertops, and modern stainless steel appliances, it's a dream come true. Step into the spacious living room that warmly welcomes you, and downstairs, discover a primary bedroom with an attached bathroom, along with a convenient laundry/mudroom.  There is a deck and oversized shed in the backyard.  And the best part?  It's situated in a central area, making accessibility a breeze!  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity.
